		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This steel mace is scribed with several runes of divine power. One side of its crushing end is marked with a rune of life, the other with a rune of final endings for the restless dead.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Mace</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +5d6 radiant critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls against undead creatures with this weapon.</li>\n<li>Whenever you reduce an enemy to 0 or fewer hit points with this weapon, a bloodied ally of your choice within 5 squares of you regains hit points equal to this weapon's enhancement bonus. If you are bloodied, you can choose to regain the hit points instead of the ally.</li>\n</ul></p>",
